        "- **(a)** $V_\\\\infty = 20\\\\,\\\\mathrm{{m/s}}$  →  $D_f = {D1_443:.2f}\\\\,\\\\mathrm{{N}}$\n",
        "- **(b)** $V_\\\\infty = 40\\\\,\\\\mathrm{{m/s}}$  →  $D_f = {D2_443:.2f}\\\\,\\\\mathrm{{N}}$\n",
        "- Exponente en $D_f \\\\propto V_\\\\infty^n$:  **$n = {n_443:.3f}$**\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
